## Modifications in This Rework

- Introduced Cognitive Execution System (CES) architecture and module boundaries.
- Added IntentEngine, ModeRouter, FusionEngine, DecisionEngine, ExecutionEngine, and MemoryGraph.
- Added prompt-aware multi-agent pipeline with strategist, architect, analyst, critic, and executor agents.
- Added runtime memory retrieval and graph-based context ranking.
- Added CES endpoints for chat/build/decision/memory analysis.
- Added auth and billing API scaffolding (JWT + refresh, OAuth endpoint scaffold, Stripe checkout).
- Added redesign scaffolding for mode-based workspace with thinking panel and command palette.

